你可以去通知皇家学会的秘书
You may inform the Secretary of the Royal Society

7
00:03:01,150 --> 00:03:05,008
我讲座的题目是
that I have entitled my lecture

8
00:03:05,046 --> 00:03:08,979
"达尔文的根本性错误"
Darwin's Fundamental Error.

9
00:03:09,016 --> 00:03:11,223
这会引发不少抗议的 先生
That'll raise a few hackles, sir.

10
00:03:12,281 --> 00:03:14,011
