别对你的未婚夫太严厉了 Presbury小姐
Do not be too severe upon your fiance Ms. Presbury.

421
00:24:29,802 --> 00:24:31,933
他已经尽了全力
He has acted for the best.

422
00:24:32,321 --> 00:24:36,287
另外 也请您继续每晚锁好门
And please will you continue to lock your door at night.

423
00:24:36,324 --> 00:24:39,228
窥视您的可不是普通的生物
The prowler who looked in upon you is no ordinary creature.

424
00:24:39,337 --> 00:24:40,154
再见
Good day.

425
00:24:44,379 --> 00:24:47,188
Jack 你不该带他到这来
Jack, you shouldn't have brought him in here.

426
00:24:47,301 --> 00:24:49,483
我没有 但他坚持要来
I didn't want to but he insisted.

427
00:24:49,597 --> 00:24:51,505
他说这里有极大的危险
He says there's grave danger.

428
00:24:51,614 --> 00:24:54,282
那是歇洛克・福尔摩斯么
Was that Sherlock Holmes?

429
00:24:54,396 --> 00:24:57,977
大侦探福尔摩斯?
The Sherlock Holmes?

430
00:24:58,083 --> 00:25:01,233
你已经观察到了这件事情的核心 华生
Your observation goes to the very heart of this business Watson.

431
00:25:01,351 --> 00:25:02,087
观察?
Observation?

432
00:25:02,123 --> 00:25:03,188
猴子和狗
Considering the monkey and the dog,

433
00:25:03,225 --> 00:25:05,272
-这就是事情的核心 -哦 你这么想?
-the very heart of it. -Oh, you think so?

434
00:25:05,310 --> 00:25:07,933
现在 如果你好心的陪我去大学
Now if you'd be so kind as to accompany me to the university

435
00:25:07,970 --> 00:25:10,100
你还可以继续去商业街
you can drive on to the Commercial Road,

436
00:25:10,136 --> 00:25:12,096
拜访一下Dorak
inquire after Dorak.

437
00:25:12,133 --> 00:25:13,857
商业街可不是个具体地址 福尔摩斯
That's not an address Holmes.

438
00:25:13,894 --> 00:25:16,641
这街有一里多长呢 从东边的Allgate一直到LimeHouse
The Commercial Road is a mile long from Allgate east to LimeHouse.

439
00:25:16,678 --> 00:25:18,739
问问小商贩 Dorak的铺子在哪
We'll ask a custom monger where Dorak's shop.

440
00:25:18,776 --> 00:25:19,741
铺子?
Shop?

441
00:25:19,778 --> 00:25:21,854
走吧 华生 我要迟到了
Come on Watson, I'm going to be late.

442
00:25:27,856 --> 00:25:31,353
在非洲 亚洲和南美洲的
The equatorial rain forests of Africa,

443
00:25:31,390 --> 00:25:32,748
热带雨林中
Asia and Southern America

444
00:25:32,859 --> 00:25:37,807
充满了常见物种的各种声音和活动
are filled with the sound and movement of a multitude of species

445
00:25:37,844 --> 00:25:39,370
以灵长目动物家族为例
from the primate family,

446
00:25:42,547 --> 00:25:44,201
这种身体活动
This physical activity,

447
00:25:44,238 --> 00:25:46,867
像在树枝上晃荡
the swinging amongst branches,

448
00:25:46,904 --> 00:25:50,232
或从一棵树的树顶 跳到另一棵树的树顶
the flying leaps from treetop to treetop

449
00:25:50,269 --> 00:25:52,964
以及发出刺耳的喊叫
and loud raucous calling,

450
00:25:53,001 --> 00:25:58,067
不仅仅是为了捍卫在森林里的势力范围
not only defines territorial rights in the forest.

451
00:25:58,177 --> 00:25:59,802
比如食物的采集
For example for food gathering,

452
00:26:00,227 --> 00:26:02,864
其中大树和灌木的嫩芽
the tender shoots of tree and shrub

453
00:26:02,976 --> 00:26:04,777
是特别的奖励
are particularly prized,

454
00:26:04,888 --> 00:26:07,484
同时也常常是
but also is frequently among

455
00:26:07,601 --> 00:26:12,155
雄性展示力量的一种仪式
the males a ritual display

456
00:26:12,262 --> 00:26:15,416
或者是为了防止不受欢迎的入侵者
either to ward off unwelcome intruders

457
00:26:15,531 --> 00:26:18,683
或者是向某一只雌性
or to impress a particular female

458
00:26:18,799 --> 00:26:22,901
展现它的性潜能
with a sexual potential of the performer.

459
00:26:23,007 --> 00:26:25,669
谢谢诸位
Thank you, gentlemen.

460
00:27:35,587 --> 00:27:38,183
- 下午好 - 你在找人么
Good afternoon, looking for somebody are ya?

461
00:27:38,300 --> 00:27:41,403
我想这附近好像有个马车行
I believe there's some livery stables here or nearby.

462
00:27:41,440 --> 00:27:44,297
没有 隔壁倒是有个妓院
No, no, we got a Macker's Yard next door,

463
00:27:44,335 --> 00:27:45,004
就这样了
that's all.

464
00:27:45,041 --> 00:27:46,904
哦 没错 你是对的
Oh, right, right you are.

465
00:27:48,326 --> 00:27:49,589
此路不通
It's a dead end.

466
00:27:49,705 --> 00:27:51,686
我看倒是可以过去
Oh, I could see a way through, yes.

467
00:27:51,793 --> 00:27:53,250
你是条子还是怎么的
You're a narc or what?

468
00:27:53,358 --> 00:27:54,982
当然不是
Not at all.

469
00:27:55,560 --> 00:27:56,880
走开
Out.

470
00:27:57,556 --> 00:27:58,076
你说什么
I'm sorry.

471
00:27:58,192 --> 00:28:00,551
我说了 走开
I said out.

472
00:28:12,408 --> 00:28:14,620
你是不肯听我的 是吧
You just can't take it in, can you?

473
00:28:14,657 --> 00:28:18,688
-你说什么? -我说了走开 你就给我乖乖的走开
-I beg your pardon? -I said out and I meant out.

474
00:28:18,726 --> 00:28:20,798
这里闲人免进 伙计
No admittance, mate.

475
00:28:20,835 --> 00:28:21,967
这可是商业场所
These are commercial premises.

476
00:28:22,084 --> 00:28:23,363
你这么说是什么意思
What do you mean by that?

477
00:28:23,474 --> 00:28:25,241
我是说这是家商店
I mean it's a shop.

478
00:28:25,352 --> 00:28:27,854
那今天肯定是很早就打烊了
It must be early closing day.

479
00:28:27,961 --> 00:28:30,664
可真够荒唐的
This is ridiculous.

480
00:28:31,202 --> 00:28:32,577
是么?
Is it?

481
00:28:38,274 --> 00:28:41,136
亲爱的Lestrade 你这样的大人物
My dear Lestrade, I'm astonished that you,

482
00:28:41,173 --> 00:28:42,412
竟来调查这么件小事
a man of your standing

483
00:28:42,449 --> 00:28:44,622
真让我惊讶
should call upon so petty an errand.

484
00:28:44,660 --> 00:28:49,114
Presbury教授对你的调查 表示了最强烈的抗议 福尔摩斯
Professor Presbury objects most strenuously to your investigations Mr. Holmes.

485
00:28:49,150 --> 00:28:53,638
他抱怨说那是缺乏正当理由的骚扰
His complaint is that of unjustified harassment.

486
00:28:53,675 --> 00:28:55,914
是否有正当理由还有待证明
The justification has yet to be proved.

487
00:28:55,952 --> 00:28:57,999
Presbury是否把事实都告诉你了?
Has Presbury informed you of the facts?

488
00:28:58,036 --> 00:28:58,696
当然
Of course.

489
00:28:58,807 --> 00:29:00,425
那你的结论是...
And your conclusions?

490
00:29:01,759 --> 00:29:04,311
这女孩在半梦半醒之间
A girl half asleep,

491
00:29:04,348 --> 00:29:08,622
将一只猫或是鸟误认为是闯入者
mistook a cat or a bird or both for an intruder.

492
00:29:08,660 --> 00:29:09,616
就是这样
That's all.

493
00:29:09,727 --> 00:29:10,965
小事一桩
It's trifle.

494
00:29:12,818 --> 00:29:14,669
就这么简单的解释?
Such a simple explanation,

495
00:29:15,462 --> 00:29:19,239
但是 这说明不了家里的那条狗的行为
however, it begs the question of the family dog, does it not?

496
00:29:19,973 --> 00:29:21,191
是不是?
Does it?

497
00:29:21,229 --> 00:29:22,100
什么狗
What dog?

498
00:29:22,213 --> 00:29:26,110
Presbury没有提及在这件事中 Roy的举止怪异么
Presbury did not mention Roy's part in this affair is strange.

499
00:29:26,147 --> 00:29:27,254
好歹Roy也算半个目击者呢
Clearly a partial witness.

500
00:29:27,291 --> 00:29:29,123
我建议你问问他
I suggest you ask him.

501
00:29:29,160 --> 00:29:31,804
你没有掌握这个复杂的案件的全部事实
You're not in full possession of the facts of this complex case.

502
00:29:31,915 --> 00:29:34,938
就算我相信你说的 这事比看上去复杂 福尔摩斯先生
Trust you to say there's more to it than meets the eye, Mr. Holmes.

503
00:29:35,045 --> 00:29:38,140
没有这种刺激的话 我就不从事这个行当了
I never concern myself in anything without that stimulus.

504
00:29:38,523 --> 00:29:41,066
但要是你一意孤行
If you persist you may find yourself

505
00:29:41,103 --> 00:29:43,768
到头来可能会被提起个人诉讼的 你知道么
at the wrong end of a private prosecution you know.

506
00:29:44,365 --> 00:29:47,007
教授是个很坚决的人
Professor Presbury is a determined man.

507
00:29:47,113 --> 00:29:49,851
那和我倒是颇为相似哦
Then we're fairly matched, are we not?

508
00:29:50,489 --> 00:29:51,943
我早知道你会是这样的
I knew it.

509
00:29:52,577 --> 00:29:54,178
好吧 我要说的都说了
Well, I've said my say.

510
00:29:54,748 --> 00:29:55,943
再见了
Mr. Holmes.

511
00:29:56,050 --> 00:29:57,602
再见
Lestrade.

512
00:30:17,334 --> 00:30:18,946
噢 你能行么?
Right, you can do it?

513
00:30:18,984 --> 00:30:21,782
是的 比在Maidstone干的那一票容易
Yeah, easier than Maidstone,

514
00:30:21,819 --> 00:30:23,509
可怜的老家伙
poor old fellow.

515
00:30:59,897 --> 00:31:05,563
商业街144号
144 Commercial Road.

516
00:31:05,674 --> 00:31:07,998
哦 你找到Dorak了 很好
Oh, you located Dorak, good.

517
00:31:08,108 --> 00:31:11,250
就我目前所知道的 表面上看来
He appears to run a general store as far as I can tell.

518
00:31:12,827 --> 00:31:14,741
他经营着一家杂货店 从熨斗到鱼钩什么都有
Sells everything from flatirons to fishhooks.

519
00:31:14,854 --> 00:31:17,035
能说的详细点么?
Can you be more specific?

520
00:31:17,149 --> 00:31:20,386
这家店生意不怎么好
Well, can't be a very prosperous business.

521
00:31:20,423 --> 00:31:21,365
为什么呢?
Why not?

522
00:31:21,402 --> 00:31:23,826
因为普通人是不让进的
Because the general public are not allowed in.

523
00:31:25,627 --> 00:31:27,745
还发现什么?
Did you discover anything else?

524
00:31:28,490 --> 00:31:30,694
除了在店旁的巷子里 被个野蛮的家伙威胁之外
Apart from being threatened by an unhelpful brute

525
00:31:30,731 --> 00:31:32,725
就没有什么了
in an alley at the side, very little.

526
00:31:32,835 --> 00:31:34,672
显然他就在那工作
He obviously works there because he followed me back

527
00:31:34,782 --> 00:31:36,583
因为他又跟着我回到了杂货店 还威胁我
to the shop and threatened me again.

528
00:31:36,694 --> 00:31:39,378
哦 还有另一个衣着光鲜的家伙
Oh, there was another fellow sharply dressed,

529
00:31:39,415 --> 00:31:42,013
穿着马甲 留着小胡子
a waistcoat with a mustache.

530
00:31:42,484 --> 00:31:43,951
叼着雪茄?
A Cheroot?

531
00:31:44,521 --> 00:31:46,409
是的 叼着雪茄
Yes, yes, he did.

532
00:31:46,446 --> 00:31:48,176
听起来像是Harry Wilcox
Sounds like Harry Wilcox,

533
00:31:48,213 --> 00:31:51,122
通常在Soho广场附近活动 而不是东区
more usually of Soho Square than the East End.

534
00:31:51,232 --> 00:31:52,082
还有什么?
Anything further?

535
00:31:52,119 --> 00:31:56,009
没什么了...除了那气味
Not really except the smell.

536
00:31:57,360 --> 00:31:59,737
那地方有种古怪的气味
There was a very odd smell about the place.

537
00:31:59,774 --> 00:32:00,848
是什么的气味?
Of what?

538
00:32:00,886 --> 00:32:02,476
不好说
Well it's not easy to say.

539
00:32:03,068 --> 00:32:05,236
有点像是什么动物的
It belonged to the animal kingdom.

540
00:32:05,273 --> 00:32:07,819
稻草或是马厩?
Straw or stables?

541
00:32:08,523 --> 00:32:10,373
更像是动物园
More like a zoo.

542
00:32:30,278 --> 00:32:31,149
你还没睡啊
You're still up.

543
00:32:31,186 --> 00:32:34,423
是的 先生 我想整理完这些论据
Yes, sir, I thought I might finish these proofs.

544
00:32:34,460 --> 00:32:37,390
你真是太尽责了 但你该去睡了
Very conscientious of you but no, no, you get to bed.

545
00:32:37,428 --> 00:32:39,057
我还是稍等会吧 先生
I'd rather not, sir.

546
00:32:39,094 --> 00:32:40,825
-我想等... -去睡觉
-I should like... -Get to bed.

547
00:32:41,847 --> 00:32:43,135
快去
Go on with you.

548
00:32:45,278 --> 00:32:48,205
好的 先生 好的
Yes, sir, very well.

549
00:32:56,586 --> 00:32:57,670
晚安 先生
Good night, sir.

550
00:32:58,321 --> 00:32:59,296
晚安
Good night.

551
00:33:45,079 --> 00:33:46,789
亲爱的 快醒醒 是我
Darling wake up, it's me.

552
00:33:49,433 --> 00:33:50,642
Edith?
Edith?

553
00:33:50,679 --> 00:33:51,234
谁啊?
Who is it?

554
00:33:51,272 --> 00:33:52,709
是我 快开门
It's me, open the door.

555
00:33:57,333 --> 00:33:58,246
怎么回事?
What is it?

556
00:33:58,282 --> 00:33:59,404
我看到了
I saw,

557
00:34:00,014 --> 00:34:01,455
没法形容
I can't describe.

