他们偷那些动物
that those animals you've rescued from degradation

749
00:48:37,430 --> 00:48:40,431
为的就是获取血清
were stolen for the sake of their glands.

750
00:48:40,874 --> 00:48:43,202
那些动物被高价买卖
The animal extract was sold at an enormous profit

751
00:48:43,238 --> 00:48:44,918
是因为有些十分愚蠢或绝望的人
to those foolish or desperate enough

752
00:48:44,956 --> 00:48:46,521
幻想用它们的血清
to imagine that a course of serum

753
00:48:46,557 --> 00:48:48,453
来恢复青春
could restore their lost vitality

754
00:48:48,490 --> 00:48:50,890
而没有其他副作用
without any other effects.

755
00:48:51,098 --> 00:48:53,290
我十分感激你 福尔摩斯先生
I am grateful to you Mr. Holmes.

756
00:48:53,327 --> 00:48:56,237
因为有你 我们才查到了犯罪的源头
Thanks to you we've traced the evil to its source.

757
00:48:56,349 --> 00:48:58,666
也许吧 可是可怜的Presbury
Perhaps, but poor Presbury.

758
00:49:00,246 --> 00:49:02,426
一个人想要凌驾于自然
When one tries to rise above nature,

759
00:49:02,539 --> 00:49:04,504
他就会堕落到丧失本性
one is liable to fall below it.

760
00:49:05,460 --> 00:49:07,440
最高等的人
The highest type of man

761
00:49:07,547 --> 00:49:09,278
一旦偏离了人类注定的轨迹
may revert to the animal

762
00:49:09,389 --> 00:49:12,743
就会变成动物
when he leaves the straight road of destiny.

763
00:49:13,076 --> 00:49:16,585
哲学上的事情还是留给你自己去想吧 福尔摩斯先生
Yes, well I'll leave the philosophy to you Mr. Holmes.

764
00:49:16,693 --> 00:49:19,056
真是明智之举 Lestrade 我一向都是这么干的
Quite the best Lestrade, I always do.

765
00:49:20,101 --> 00:49:21,724
那条爱尔兰猎狗要人道毁灭么?
Is the wolfhound to be destroyed?

766
00:49:21,841 --> 00:49:25,857
不 不 Roy攻击的是猴子 而不是人
Oh, no, no it was the monkey that Roy attacked, not the man.

767
00:49:25,893 --> 00:49:29,050
狗会和他的主人一样都恢复原样的
But the dog will be himself again quite as much as his master.

768
00:49:30,434 --> 00:49:33,103
谢谢二位
Well, thank you both.

769
00:49:33,787 --> 00:49:34,996
再见 先生们
Good day, gentlemen.

770
00:49:35,033 --> 00:49:36,521
再见 Lestrade
Good day Lestrade.

771
00:49:39,531 --> 00:49:40,930
如果我可以这么说的话 福尔摩斯
If I my say so Holmes

772
00:49:41,037 --> 00:49:44,374
我觉得你给予Lestrade过多的功劳了
I think you went a little too far in allowing Lestrade all the credit.

773
00:49:44,411 --> 00:49:45,692
不全是这样 华生
Not all Watson.

774
00:49:46,471 --> 00:49:49,104
你可以把它存在我们的办案记录里
You can file it away in our archives.

775
00:49:49,142 --> 00:49:52,316
总有为人所知的那一天的
One day the entire truth can be told.

776
